\c 31
\s Joshua anofanira kutevera Mozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Mozisi wakaenda ndokutaura mashoko awa kuna Israeri wese,
\v 2 ndokuti kwavari: Ndine makore zana nemakumi maviri nhasi\x + 34.7. Eki. 7.7.\x*; handichagonizve kubuda nekupinda\x + Num. 27.17.\x*; zvino Jehovha wakati kwandiri: Haungayambuki Joridhani urwu\x + 3.27. Num. 20.12. 27.13.\x*.
\v 3 Jehovha Mwari wako ndiye achayambuka mberi kwako; ndiye achaparadza marudzi awa kubva pamberi pako, uye uchaagara nhaka; Joshua ndiye achayambuka pamberi pako\x + 9.3.\x*, Jehovha sezvaakataura\x + 3.28. Num. 27.21.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha achaita kwavari\x + 3.21.\x* sezvaakaita kuna Sihoni nekuna Ogi madzimambo eVaAmori, nekunyika yavo, vaakaparadza\x + Num. 21.23,24,33,35.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino Jehovha achavapa pamberi pechiso chenyu, kuti muite kwavari zvichienderana nemurairo wose wandakakurairai\x + 7.2.\x*.
\v 6 Simbai, uye tsungai\x + 7,23. 3.28. Josh. 1.6,7,9. 10.25. 1 Makor. 22.13. 28.20.\x*, musatya kana kuvhunduswa pamberi pezviso zvavo\x + 1.29; 7.18,21; 20.3.\x*; nokuti Jehovha Mwari wako ndiye anoenda newe\x + 20.4.\x*; haangakurasi kana kukusiya\x + 31.8. Josh. 1.5.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Mozisi wakadana kuna Joshua ndokuti kwaari pameso aIsraeri wese: Simba uye tsunga, nokuti iwe uchapinda nevanhu ava panyika Jehovha yaakapikira madzibaba avo kuvapa, uye iwe uchavagarisa nhaka iyo\x + 31.6,23.\x*.
\v 8 NaJehovha ndiye anofamba mberi kwako; iye achava newe\x + 9.3. Eki. 13.21.\x*; haangakurasi kana kukusiya; usatya\x + 31.8. Josh. 1.5.\x* uye usavhunduswa\x + 1.21; Josh. 1.9. 8.1. 10.25. Det. 7.18.\x*.
\s Murairo unofanira kuverengwa pakupera kwemakore manomwe
\p
\v 9 Zvino Mozisi wakanyora murairo uyu ndokuupa kuvapristi vanakomana vaRevhi\x + 17.18.\x*, vaitakura areka yesungano yaJehovha, nekuvakuru vose vaIsraeri\x + 31.25. Num. 4.15. Josh. 3.3. 8.33. 1 Makor. 15.15.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino Mozisi wakavaraira achiti: Pakupera kwemakore manomwe, panguva yakatarwa yegore resununguro\x + 15.1,2,9.\x*, pamutambo wemisasa\x + Rev. 23.34.\x*,
\v 11 apo Israeri wose auya kuonekwa pamberi paJehovha Mwari wako panzvimbo yaachasarudza\x + 16.16.\x*, uchaverenga murairo uyu pamberi paIsraeri wose munzeve dzavo\x + Josh. 8.34,35. 2 Madz. 23.2. Neh. 8.1-3.\x*.
\v 12 Unganidza vanhu, varume, nevakadzi, nevanana, nemutorwa wako ari pakati pemasuwo ako, kuti vanzwe, uye kuti vadzidze, vagotya Jehovha Mwari wenyu, vachengetedze kuita mashoko ose emurairo uyu\x + 4.10.\x*.
\v 13 Uye vana vavo vasingazivi\x + 11.2.\x* vanzwe, vagodzidza kutya Jehovha Mwari wenyu mazuva ose amuchagara panyika yamunoyambuka Joridhani kuenda kwairi kunoigara nhaka\x + Map. 78.5,6.\x*.
\s VaIsraeri vachatsauka panzira dzaJehovha
\p
\v 14 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Tarira, mazuva ako ekufa aswedera\x + 31.2,16.\x*; dana Joshua mugozvimisa mutende rekusangana, kuti ndimuraire. Mozisi naJoshua ndokuenda ndokuzvimisa mutende rekusangana\x + 31.23. Num. 27.19.\x*.
\v 15 Jehovha ndokuonekwa mutende mushongwe yegore; zvino shongwe yegore yakamira pamusoro pemukova wetende\x + Eki. 33.9.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Tarira, ucharara nemadzibaba ako; zvino vanhu ava vachasimuka\x + Eki. 32.6.\x* ndokufeva vachitevera vamwari vevatorwa venyika kwavanoendamo pakati pavo\x + Eki. 34.15.\x*; uye vachandisiya\x + Vato. 2.12. 10.6,13.\x* nekuputsa sungano yangu yandakaita navo\x + 31.20. Vato. 2.1. Rev. 26.15.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino kutsamwa kwangu kuchavapfutira nezuva iro; uye ndichavasiya\x + 2 Makor. 15.2. 24.20.\x* nekuvavanzira chiso changu, vachava zvekudya\x + 32.20. Map. 30.7. 104.29. Isa. 8.17. 64.7. Eze. 39.23. Isa. 59.2.\x*, nezvakaipa zvizhinji nematambudziko zvichavawira; kusvika vati nezuva iro: Zvakaipa izvi hazvina kutiwira nokuti Mwari wedu haasi pakati pedu here\x + Num. 14.42.\x*?
\v 18 Zvino ini ndichavanza chiso changu zvirokwazvo nezuva iro nekuda kwezvakaipa zvose zvavakaita, nokuti vakatsaukira kune vamwe vamwari\x + 31.17.\x*.
\v 19 Naizvozvo ikozvino zvinyorerei rwiyo urwu, murwudzidzise kuvana vaIsraeri, murwuise mumuromo wavo, kuti rwiyo urwu rwuve uchapupu kwandiri hwakamirisana nevana vaIsraeri\x + 31.21,26.\x*.
\v 20 Nokuti ndavapinza panyika yandakapikira madzibaba avo, inoyerera mukaka neuchi, zvino vadya ndokuguta\x + Eki. 3.8.\x*, vakorawo\x + 32.15.\x*, zvino vachatsaukira kune vamwe vamwari ndokuvashumira\x + 31.18.\x*, ndokundizvidza\x + Num. 14.11,23. 16.30.32.19.\x* nekuputsa sungano yangu\x + 31.20. Vato. 2.1. Rev. 26.15.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino zvichaitika kana zvakaipa zvizhinji nematambudziko zvavawira, kuti rwiyo urwu rwuchapupura kuzviso zvavo kuva chapupu; nokuti harwungakanganikwi kubva pamuromo wembeu yavo\x + 31.17.\x*, nokuti ndinoziva\x + Hos. 5.3. 13.5,6.\x* murangariro wavanoita nhasi ndisati ndavapinza munyika yandinopikira\x + Gen.. 6.5.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Zvino Mozisi wakanyora rwiyo urwu nezuva iro, ndokurwudzidzisa vana vaIsraeri.
\v 23 Zvino wakaraira Joshua mwanakomana waNuni ndokuti\x + 31.14.\x*: Simba, utsunge, nokuti iwe uchapinza vana vaIsraeri panyika yandakavapikira\x + 31.6.\x*; neni ndichava newe\x + 31.8.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Zvino zvakaitika Mozisi apedza kunyora mashoko emurairo uyu mubhuku, kusvika apera\x + 31.9.\x*,
\v 25 kuti Mozisi wakaraira VaRevhi vaitakura areka yesungano yaJehovha achiti\x + 31.9.\x*:
\v 26 Torai bhuku iri remurairo, muriise parutivi rweareka yesungano yaJehovha Mwari wenyu, kuti rivepo\x + 2 Madz.22.8.\x* kuva uchapupu hwakamirisana newe\x + 31.19,21.\x*.
\v 27 Nokuti ini ndinoziva upanduki hwako, nemutsipa wako mukukutu; tarirai, ini ndichiri mupenyu pamwe nemwi nhasi\x + Eki. 32.9.\x*, manga muri vapanduki kuna Jehovha; zvino zvikuru shure kwekufa kwangu\x + 9.7,24.\x*!
\p
\v 28 Ndiunganidzire vakuru vose vemarudzi enyu nevatungamiriri venyu, kuti nditaure mashoko awa munzeve dzavo\x + 16.18.\x*, uye ndidane matenga nepasi kuva zvapupu zvakamirisana navo\x + 30.19. 32.1.\x*.
\v 29 Nokuti ndinoziva kuti shure kwekufa kwangu muchava vakaora kwazvo uye muchatsauka panzira yandinokurairai\x + 32.5. Vato. 2.19. Hos. 9.9.\x*; uye kuipa kuchakuwira pakuguma kwemazuva; nokuti muchaita zvakaipa pameso aJehovha\x + 4.30; Gen..49.1.\x* kuti mumutsamwise nebasa remaoko enyu\x + 4.25. 9.18. 32.16,21. Det. 32.19,27. Vato. 2.12. 1 Sam. 1.6,7.\x*.
\p
\v 30 Zvino Mozisi wakataura mashoko erwiyo urwu munzeve dzeungano yose yaIsraeri, kusvika apera.